profile:
Timkha Chem-Dry is proud to serve our community every day through our affordable eco-friendly cleaning services. We are committed to helping residents of Oakville, Burlington, Hamilton, Niagara Falls, Milton, and the surrounding areas maintain a healthy and happy home, all year round. Through a combination of our proprietary process and our non-toxic, green-certified solution, we guarantee that we’ll leave your home with a long-lasting clean.

Our expert technicians are dedicated to providing unbeatable cleaning services. When you put your trust in us, you can feel confident that you’re receiving a reliable clean that lasts.

Chem-Dry’s mission is helping people live healthy lives starting with clean carpets and a healthy home. Our proprietary Hot Carbonating Extraction cleaning process penetrates deep into the fibers, removing an average of 98% of common household allergens from carpets and upholstery and 89% of the airborne bacteria in your home when a sanitizer is added.*

Our green-certified solution, The Natural®, contains no dirt attracting soaps or detergents so it’s safe and non-toxic for your family & pets. And, Chem-Dry uses 80% less water than typical steam cleaning so carpets dry in hours instead of days, making it the safer and more convenient carpet cleaning choice. All of this means Chem-Dry cleans for your health like no one else.
services:
Professional cleaning services for the following:
- Carpet
- Upholstery
- Area Rugs
- Tile and grout
- Hardwood floor
